            {
                "comment": "Palta is an interesting character.  I learned more in this class than any other agriculture/biology related course.  It was amazing.  Tests are very specific (you need to memorize exact values) but he gives you study guides and uses the same exams every year.  Try to get your hands on a previous copy.  It helps!  Good class! No homework.",
